<h1><span>Usage</span></h1>
<p>This is a Black Highlighter based theme, meaning you will need to import the Black Highlighter theme as well in order to use this theme. To learn more, go <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/component:black-highlighter-theme-dev">here</a>.</p>
<p><strong>To import this theme, simply add the following to your page:</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki:theme:the-coalition-theme]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
